#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.absolute.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.absolute"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute:1 of
msgid "Calculate the absolute value element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算绝对值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播至输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字"
"参数）的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.absolute.absolute:15 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**absolute** -- An tensor containing the absolute value of each element "
"in `x`.  For complex input, ``a + ib``, the absolute value is "
":math:`\\sqrt{ a^2 + b^2 }`."
msgstr ""
"**absolute** -- 一个包含 `x` 中每个元素绝对值的 tensor。对于复数输入 ``a "
"+ ib``，其绝对值为 :math:`\\sqrt{ a^2 + b^2 }`。"

